{"text": " At the heart of our practice is the development of the silent mind. It is a practical method to reduce fluctuations of consciousness and cultivate a profound sense of stability and self-consolidation. It starts from a basic observation. Most of us spend the day constantly engaging with many objects and many thoughts. It causes our mental, emotional and physical potential to be divided into a thousand things. In silent mind, we bring consciousness back to ourselves and develop sense of wholeness and self-consolidation. We reduce random mind-wondering through self-awareness and sustained attention. Even short moments of this state can enhance our clarity and sense of inner fulfillment. With continued practice, we can live better by transforming from within and empowering for a lifetime, yourself and the others.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 6.760000000000004, "end": 13.2, "text": " At the heart of our practice is the development of the silent mind.", "tokens": [50364, 1711, 264, 1917, 295, 527, 3124, 307, 264, 3250, 295, 264, 12784, 1575, 13, 51294], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1663526647231158, "compression_ratio": 1.3893805309734513, "no_speech_prob": 0.03815815970301628, "words": [{"word": " At", "start": 6.760000000000004, "end": 7.96, "probability": 0.6429117918014526}, {"word": " the", "start": 7.96, "end": 8.14, "probability": 0.9835732579231262}, {"word": " heart", "start": 8.14, "end": 8.36, "probability": 0.9973453879356384}, {"word": " of", "start": 8.36, "end": 8.58, "probability": 0.9976744055747986}, {"word": " our", "start": 8.58, "end": 8.72, "probability": 0.9930435419082642}, {"word": " practice", "start": 8.72, "end": 9.16, "probability": 0.9772711396217346}, {"word": " is", "start": 9.16, "end": 10.1, "probability": 0.833820104598999}, {"word": " the", "start": 10.1, "end": 10.24, "probability": 0.9881447553634644}, {"word": " development", "start": 10.24, "end": 10.78, "probability": 0.9946157336235046}, {"word"